Adrianne Allen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrianne_Allen 0 Adrianne Allen (7 February 1907 – 14 September 1993) was an English stage actress.Most often seen in light comedy, played Sybil Chase in the original West End production of Private Lives and Elizabeth Bennet in the 1935 Broadway production of Pride and Prejudice. She appeared in several films and was the mother of actors Daniel and Anna Massey.
